{"tid":818232,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人用過Rocketbook, 好唔好用","createTime":"2018-09-14T03:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T16:50:59.000Z","uid":49178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"97fdc518c2eac8238575e4412eb93717aa1f027b","tid":818232,"uid":49178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T03:28:38.000Z","msg":"-可循環筆記簿<br />\n-獨家的專利圖像擷取技術，能供精準的翻拍筆記內容<br />\n-使用普通商店也可買到的Pilot Frixion魔擦鋼珠筆<br />\n<br />\n聽就好似唔錯，但係係唔係真係咁好用？<br />\n有無巴打絲打試過？定用原始好<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U9Kas8l38Kc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU9Kas8l38Kc&d=rAai0gMwKAq3%2B1w65DxwjDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4d9b2693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U9Kas8l38Kc</a>"},{"pid":"e0971547cc0ded2df7356a11eaaa3e9aa400e4fb","tid":818232,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"基本冇用，唯一有既特別功能係個cloud server, 畀你影完張note放上去，同影果陣有個qr code畀你對位<br />\n<br />\n但全部功能都可以用現有既野做到，加熱會甩色既墨水筆普通文具鋪就有，影相用可以隨便一個scanner app"},{"pid":"29c669d6f25a7b68e37cd9a25a26900a18b76320","tid":818232,"uid":149613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616895d80436c62d842fbd9bd807d0a9d32835ad","tid":818232,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"花巧嘢"}]}